<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="2148">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yuan-he-88-65" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yuan-he-88-65" class="zg-link" title="风荷举">风荷举</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yu-ban-de-gu-tai" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yu-ban-de-gu-tai" class="zg-link" title="御坂的呱太">御坂的呱太</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yan-xuan-29" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yan-xuan-29" class="zg-link" title="言酒浅">言酒浅</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


