<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="438">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhu-ce-gei-xiao-nian-ge-ge-kan" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhu-ce-gei-xiao-nian-ge-ge-kan" class="zg-link" title="注册给小年哥哥看">注册给小年哥哥看</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$shuang-tian-23" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/shuang-tian-23" class="zg-link" title="霜天">霜天</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$li-lin-feng-98-93" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/li-lin-feng-98-93" class="zg-link" title="李林峰">李林峰</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3263987" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">顺口溜而已，比较文艺，但压根不着调。看我接——<br><br><b>“快拿木盆来！可赶上这波！”</b>（请自行脑补天津口音）<br><br>向 <a data-hash="59fcae62596fb6ba08f2860a5fe6f171" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/59fcae62596fb6ba08f2860a5fe6f171" class="member_mention" data-tip="p$b$59fcae62596fb6ba08f2860a5fe6f171">@Kaiser</a> 神致敬！


</div>

